name: Warung Pan Dodol
address: Jl. Kwanji Gg. Walet No.4, Ketewel, Kec. Sukawati, Kabupaten Gianyar, Bali 80582, Indonesia
review 1:
The best balinese food in ketewel. Its a new balinese restaurant with its signature menu, lawar. The restaurant located in its owner house. They have plenty of tables and chairs. They open from 5 pm - finish. The finish time can be at 9pm or 8pm depends according to the order from the guest.

My personal observation based on scale 1 to 5, from very bad, bad, okay, good, very good.

Taste: 5/5
Price: 4/5
Parking area: 3/5
Staff: 5/5
Location: 5/5
Recommended: yes absolutely, one of the best balinese food can be found here. Been here twice in a month ü§ü

name: Warung Bu Devi Lawar Marlin
address: Jl. Kwanji, Ketewel, Kec. Sukawati, Kabupaten Gianyar, Bali 80582, Indonesia
review 1:
First time eating Lawar Marlin and boy it was super legit. Not disappointing at all despite the slightly expensive price (compared to other local dish).
Every meal consist: jackfruit marlin (fish) lawar; raw marlin lawar (plek); komoh marlin (fish soup), serapah marlin (fish seasoned with spices, coconut milk & rice flour), fish satay (wrap & skewer style), vegetables also a HILL size of rice, lol.
It cost me 30K rupiah for a meal (without drink). And as the locals said Jaen Sajan, believe me, it‚Äôs worth every penny!!
